review_blob: Just a stronger version of a beer that has no right to the name it claims I thought this would be a fad but it seems to be sticking around

No time for long explanations, for the price I cant complain. Nothing to write home about but its clean, refreshing and good for a hot day. A bit of skunky smell but not in taste. Reminds me of Landshark but actuallty worth drinking. Cheers all
